<body ng-app="starter" ng-controller="actionsheetCtl" >
	<ion-pane>
	    <ion-content >
	        <h2 ng-click="action()">$ionicBackdrop</h2>
	    </ion-content>
	</ion-pane>
</body>
```
同样是angular的移动平台方案
[更多](http://www.runoob.com/ionic/ionic-tutorial.html)

