align-self属性允许单个项目有与其他项目不一样的对齐方式，可覆盖align-items属性。默认值为auto，表示继承父元素的align-items属性，如果没有父元素，则等同于stretch。

``` bash
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title></title>
    <style type="text/css">

        .flex_start{
            display: flex;

            align-items: flex-start;
            height: 80px;
            background: red;
        }
        .flex_start div:last-child{
            align-self:flex-end;
        }

         .flex_stretch{
            display: flex;

            height: 80px;
            align-items: stretch;
            background: orange;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="flex_start">
    <div>1</div>
    <div>2</div>
    <div>3</div>
    <div>4</div>
</div>

<div class="flex_stretch">
    <div>1</div>
    <div>2</div>
    <div>3</div>
    <div>4</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
```

